OL,3,CReality TV risks 'crossing line into
OL,4,Cexploitation', former Ofcom chair says
OL,6,FReality television producers are in
OL,7,Fjeopardy of "crossing a line into
OL,8,Fexploitation and taking risks with the
OL,9,Fpublic's mental health", the former
OL,10,Fchairman of regulator Ofcom has said.
OL,12,FLord Grade's remarks follow
OL,13,Fallegations of rape and sexual assault
OL,14,Fmade by former contestants of Channel
OL,15,F4's Married At First Sight UK (MAFS
OL,16,FUK), as shown in a BBC Panorama
OL,17,Fdocumentary.
OL,26,@oD@MOUqD@WO]
