OL,3,CReality TV risks 'crossing line into
OL,4,Cexploitation', former Ofcom chair says
OL,6,FTui Group announced on Thursday that
OL,7,Fit had ended its sponsorship of the UK
OL,8,Fand Australian versions of the show,
OL,9,Ffollowing the emergence of the
OL,10,Fallegations.
OL,12,FLord Grade said participants of such
OL,13,Fshows "know what's in store, but they
OL,14,Fcan't possibly imagine what emotional
OL,15,Froller coasters they're going to have
OL,16,Fto go through and their ability to
OL,17,Fwithstand and manage those roller
OL,18,Fcoasters".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
