OL,3,CReality TV risks 'crossing line into
OL,4,Cexploitation', former Ofcom chair says
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe broadcaster announced the launch
OL,12,Fof Second Marriage At First Sight in
OL,13,FFebruary, which hopes to bring
OL,14,Ftogether contestants from the UK and
OL,15,FAustralian versions of the show for a
OL,16,Fsecond chance at love.
OL,18,FOn Tuesday police urged potential
OL,19,Fvictims of sexual assault on the TV
OL,20,Fshow to come forward.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
