OL,3,CReality TV risks 'crossing line into
OL,4,Cexploitation', former Ofcom chair says
OL,6,FShortly before the Panorama episode
OL,7,Faired, Channel 4 announced it had
OL,8,Fcommissioned an external review into
OL,9,Fcontributor welfare last month.
OL,11,FLawyers for CPL, the independent
OL,12,Fproduction company that makes the UK
OL,13,Fversion of the show, told Panorama its
OL,14,Fwelfare system was "gold standard" and
OL,15,Fthat it acted appropriately in all
OL,16,Fthese cases.
